Advise females of reproductive potential that effective contraception should be used during treatment and for 4 weeks following the final dose of RINVOQ/RINVOQ LQ  [see Use in Specific Populations (

                        8.3

                     )].

Advise women exposed to RINVOQ/RINVOQ LQ during pregnancy that there is a pregnancy surveillance program that monitors pregnancy outcomes [see Use in Specific Populations (

                        8.1

                     )].

Advise women not to breastfeed during treatment with RINVOQ/RINVOQ LQ and for 6 days after the last dose [see Use in Specific Populations (

                        8.2

